data.description: Do to Relocation SELLERS are MOTIVATED!! You don't want to miss this home on OVER AN ACRE & NO HOA! Adorable and spacious 3-bedroom 2-bath home with lots of potential. It has a split floor plan with the owneras suite and bathroom on one side. Master Bath has a garden tub, separate shower, and large walk-in closet. Two other bedrooms on the opposite side of the home. Spacious kitchen with a large eat-in area and separate dining area. The living room has high ceilings and a gas fireplace. Large Front porch with a swing for relaxing. The back yard has a utility shed and plenty of room for animals, a garden, children to run and play, boats, an RV and ATVs. A new well was installed in 2022.
